<plot>Ruins is a sentimental drama which tells the story of Ben a young German archaeologist who works in Rome, Italy. While his girlfriend July visits him he accidentally meets Marianna, his first big love never forgotten. This encounter makes him dig into his personal past, trying to get over it and live his present life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?470209</url></doc>
